                      "name": "obP1",
                      "fill": "$ink-soft",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "When you dictate a clinical narrative describing a patient's death, CODA transcribes what you say and surfaces probabilistic causes of death in real time. All processing happens on your device.",
